The paper discusses abstraction techniques for ordinary differential equations (ODEs) used in modelling dynamical systems. This topic falls under the category of systems and control (cs.SY). The paper also discusses the use of equivalence relations and labelled transition systems, which are topics in logic (cs.LO) and programming languages (cs.PL). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of machine learning techniques for ODE reduction, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.MS) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
